fields.name: Anti Nuke Settings
fields.value: You can check anti nuke settings using the `/settings anti nuke`

fields.name: Action Limits
fields.value: You can set a limit to the dangerous actions using the `/setlimit` command

fields.name: Action Punishments
fields.value: Punishments will be applied when someone reaches the limit of a dangerous action, set punishments using `/setpunishment`

fields.name: Enable/Disable Actions
fields.value: You can disable or enable some actions using `/enable` and `/disable`
